cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF to an unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause AMF connection failure, preventing NG interface communication and leading to system initialization failure.

du.explanation_en: Changing Ta4 from [110, 180] to [180, 110] creates timing misalignment where the upper bound is less than the lower bound, causing logical contradiction in front-haul timing parameters and potential synchronization errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Ta4 從 [110, 180] 更改為 [180, 110] 會導致時序錯位，其中上限小於下限，造成前傳時序參數中的邏輯矛盾，並可能導致同步錯誤。
